name: Honor
author: David Rafael Ruiz Blanco
body:
Beschrijving

Cargo ship with remains of ship structure visible over the sand . Massive presence of armament, ordnance, cargo consist in textils and pewter elements.

Status

Partially destroyed by dredging and buried in sand
